io.elegie.luchess.core.domain.moves.processors

Class MoveResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.elegie.luchess.core.domain.moves.processors.MoveResolver

  • public class MoveResolver
extends java.lang.Object
    A move resolver is used to find and build a move object, given a particular position, a starting vertex, an ending vertex, and an optional promotion figurine (for pawn moves).
